parameters:
Woman: Seriously, what kind of training do you give your
part-timers?! This place is outrageous!!! It's so
unpleasant!!! I'll spread the word among my mommy friends
and ruin your reputation!!

Cerberus Octopus: Eek... uh, about the cookie in my
pocket... ah, no, never mind... It was our mistake! I'm
terribly sorry!!

Memimi: (She's broken... That lady is too strong... Even if
I had been dealing with her, I'd probably be crying by
now...)

Woman: Do you think an apology is enough!? Show some remorse
for goodness sake!! Get naked and prostrate yourself! Naked
prostration!!!

Cerberus Octopus, as the manager of Jagged Mart, was forced
to take responsibility in a humiliating manner...

Woman: I'll punish you for treating me like a thief!! I'll
record it and upload it to the net, so hurry up and strip!!!
Prostrate! Prostrate!!

Memimi: Ce... Cerberus Octopus, there's no need to listen to
her! We don't need to treat her like a customer anymore...
this is clear business interference, it's practically
extortion!

Cerberus Octopus: The part-timer should shut up... I have no
obligation to be worried about by the likes of you! If I bow
my head, that should settle it... Apologies, I'll give as
many as you want!!

Memimi: Cerberus Octopus... perhaps I have misunderstood you
a little... Indeed, you are also a respectable boss of an
organization, a man of principle...

Customer: Why isn't it Memimi-chan who's stripping... Who
wants to see Cerberus Octopus's naked prostration?! It makes
no sense...

Cerberus Octopus: Hah hah... being uploaded to the net,
what's the big deal...! Even the Shark Duke would... ugh...!

Cerberus Octopus: Tch... nobody has ever seen my true form,
and to think it would be revealed in a place like this...

Cerberus Octopus: I'm very sorry... Please let this be
enough...

Woman: Hah hah... keep prostrating yourself just like that!!
I'm recording this, streaming it live on the net!!
Memimi: Um... please, forgive him already... It's pitiful...

Cerberus Octopus: You have no right to worry about me!! Shut
up! This is nothing to me at all!!

Customer: That's Cerberus Octopus for you...! Even while
performing a naked prostration, he maintains such a
dignified attitude! ...Wait, wasn't that guy working part-
time at a ramen shop?

Customer: Ah, I've seen him before. He's that guy who goes
to Mudane University. He's juggling several part-time jobs
at eateries and is known as a hardworking student.

Customer: His family runs a boxing gym, right? And they're
not doing too well with the business. Even as the boss of a
big organization, he's got his struggles...
